      "So I need to write thoughts down.\nIf I do not, they will scatter, be forgotten, and lose the chance to keep growing.",
      "But I also cannot fully trust the written versions.\nBecause they are not thought itself, only the shape of thought after being compressed at a certain moment.",
      "They help me preserve thought.\nThey also help me organize thought.\nBut they also shape how I will think afterward.",
      "I need to be reminded by them.\nAnd I need to continue moving out of them."
